org.mitre.tdp.boogie.alg.resolve

Class GraphableLeg

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.tdp.boogie.alg.resolve.GraphableLeg

  • public class GraphableLeg
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a graph node as a SectionSplit as extracted from the top level route string, a top level resolved infrastructure element associated with that split ResolvedElement and a leg indicating both what the fix is as well as an indication of how to fly to it.

    e.g. For airways the expanded legs are LegType.TF while for ..FIX.. elements the leg type is indicated as LegType.IF while for procedures they are as declared in the procedure definition.
